snippet.title: Ad Fundum - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The demo of our platformer Ad Fundum is available now on Steam! Download it, play it and if you enjoy the game, don't forget to add it to your wishlist!

Link to the game can be found in the channel description.
